==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[θεραπεία]]''' (''therapeia'') "attendance, treatment, healing, service", from '''[[θεραπεύω]]''' (''therapeuo'') "to attend, to treat, to heal, to cure, to serve".

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''therapy''' (''plural'' therapies)
#[[Treatment]] of [[disease]] or [[disability]]
#[[Healing]] [[power]] or [[quality]]
